sub_title: Responsive Business Intelligence Intern at Nike | Data Visualization | Insight & Analytics
summary:
A graduate student of Business Informatics at University of Ljubljana currently employed as a full time Intern at Nike. As an organised and detail-oriented person, I have more than several years of work experience. 

Most recent job activities include:
- Tableau analysis and visualisation of data, building dashboard reporting solutions
- Assisting the team with SQL assignments in Snowflake, building applications with Microsoft PowerApps
- Taking on Scrum master hat, leading daily stand-ups and sprint retrospectives 
- Building and updating team space on Confluence 
- Administrative tasks
